commit.title: Make Travis faster by removing more builds.
commit.message:
Make Travis faster by removing more builds.

We remove all the testing of external projects from Travis.
The current state was inconsistent anyways.
We keep the matrix of test-suite / validate / warnings / doc targets
with different OCaml version.
If people want to do more thorough testing on their personal branches,
they will have to setup GitLab CI as explained in dev/ci/README.md.
It's not difficult to setup.
